SUPER HANG-ON:

        Beat the highest score for a continent and enter "750J" for your
        name on the high score table.  Hold down the 'CTRL', 'LEFT ALT',
        'Z', and 'T' as the credits change.  Let go of the the keys to
        activate the cheat.  Press the 'AMIGA KEY' to activate the machine
        guns.  Enter new coefficiants for the road turns using the keypad.
        The initial settings are 60 and 45.

